# Layout Comparison: Sidebar vs Minimalist Design

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Layout1["❌ REJECTED: Fixed Sidebar Layout (Intrusive)"]
        S1[Search History Sidebar<br/>280px wide]
        S2[Settings Panel<br/>280px wide]
        S3[Force Graph<br/>Reduced width]
        S1 -.-> S3
        S2 -.-> S3
    end

    subgraph Layout2["✅ RECOMMENDED: Minimalist Layout (Unobtrusive)"]
        M1[Search Bar<br/>Centered]
        M2[Semantic Filters<br/>Collapsible left panel]
        M3[Force Graph<br/>Full width]
        M2 -.optional.-> M3
    end

    subgraph Layout3["✅ RECOMMENDED: Contextual Controls (Reveal on Demand)"]
        C1[Search Bar]
        C2[Force Graph]
        C3[Hover: Node Details]
        C4[Click: Highlight Neighbors]
        C5[Double-click: Zoom Community]
        C3 -.on demand.-> C2
        C4 -.on demand.-> C2
        C5 -.on demand.-> C2
    end

    style S1 fill:#FF4400,color:#FFF
    style S2 fill:#FF4400,color:#FFF
    style S3 fill:#FF9999,color:#000
    style M1 fill:#00AA00,color:#FFF
    style M2 fill:#00AA00,color:#FFF
    style M3 fill:#99FF99,color:#000
    style C1 fill:#00AA00,color:#FFF
    style C2 fill:#99FF99,color:#000
    style C3 fill:#00AA00,color:#FFF
    style C4 fill:#00AA00,color:#FFF
    style C5 fill:#00AA00,color:#FFF
```

## Layout Comparison Table

| Aspect | Fixed Sidebar | Minimalist | Contextual |
|--------|---------------|------------|------------|
| **Graph Width** | 60-70% (reduced) | 100% (full) | 100% (full) |
| **UI Clutter** | High (persistent) | Low (collapsible) | Very Low (on-demand) |
| **User Learning** | Medium (discover features) | Low (self-explanatory) | Very Low (intuitive) |
| **Rams Compliance** | 2/10 ❌ | 10/10 ✅ | 10/10 ✅ |
| **Implementation** | 5 days | 3 days | 2 days |

## Visual Impact

### Fixed Sidebar (REJECTED)
